-- millhaven-5.cell: Gate 1 вЂ” 5 citizens + 1 analyst in Millhaven
-- Each citizen lives a day in the city. The analyst studies them.

-- City context: shared world-state that all citizens inhabit
вЉў city
  yield description в‰Ў "Millhaven is a small coastal town of about 5,000 people. It has a harbor district with fishing boats and seafood restaurants, a main street with shops and a library, a residential hill with Victorian houses, a community park with a bandstand, and an old lighthouse on the point. The weather today is overcast with occasional drizzle. It is a Tuesday in early March."
  yield population в‰Ў 5
  yield day в‰Ў "Tuesday, March 4"

